descriptionNullable:
### Context

There's a story behind every dataset and here's your opportunity to share yours.


### Content

What's inside is more than just rows and columns. Make it easy for others to get started by describing how you acquired the data and what time period it represents, too.


### Acknowledgements

This dataset is from [互联网新闻情感分析](https://www.datafountain.cn/competitions/350/datasets). I upload this to help us do further research on these. If there are any copyright issues, please contact me to delete the file.


### Inspiration

Your data will be in front of the world's largest data science community. What questions do you want to see answered?
